    "description": "<br>Welcome to Shooting Range Simulator! <br><br>Ever dreamed of running your own shooting range? Now's your chance. Manage your business, from selling ammo and renting out weapons to upgrading your facilities and expanding your inventory. Buy supplies online, attract customers, and watch your range thrive. It's all about precision, strategy, and making your mark. Ready to take aim?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Range Design</h2>Craft your shooting range and its store, balancing both functionality and style. Arrange targets, set up shooting lanes, and create an environment that offers a top-notch experience for your patrons.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013490/extras/c3dc9e1d302d4c5c7097381231b63143.poster.avif?t=1729021181\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013490/extras/c3dc9e1d302d4c5c7097381231b63143.webm?t=1729021181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013490/extras/c3dc9e1d302d4c5c7097381231b63143.mp4?t=1729021181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stock Management</h2>Order a variety of targets, firearms, ammos and accessories using an in-game computer. Organize your inventory efficiently in the storage room and ensure the range is always well-stocked and ready for action.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013490/extras/f52948ee1c1a855a7195d822af0b5647.poster.avif?t=1729021181\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013490/extras/f52948ee1c1a855a7195d822af0b5647.webm?t=1729021181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013490/extras/f52948ee1c1a855a7195d822af0b5647.mp4?t=1729021181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customer Service</h2>Assist customers with selecting firearms, provide safety briefings, and handle payments. Ensure every visitor has a safe, enjoyable, and memorable experience at your range.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013490/extras/83486c001059d2091ac6f1d0d0733cdc.poster.avif?t=1729021181\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013490/extras/83486c001059d2091ac6f1d0d0733cdc.webm?t=1729021181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013490/extras/83486c001059d2091ac6f1d0d0733cdc.mp4?t=1729021181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Special Weapons Ordering</h2>Unlock and order special types of weapons, from antique firearms to cutting-edge prototypes. Offer your customers a unique experience with these exclusive items.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013490/extras/aa0af8964554980a7c1df82017218d35.poster.avif?t=1729021181\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013490/extras/aa0af8964554980a7c1df82017218d35.webm?t=1729021181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013490/extras/aa0af8964554980a7c1df82017218d35.mp4?t=1729021181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Weapon Maintenance</h2>Disassemble weapons and clean their parts to ensure they remain safe and functional. Regular maintenance is key to keeping your inventory in top condition and preventing malfunctions.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013490/extras/f0dc5336abf293d68280bbd96c39d670.poster.avif?t=1729021181\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013490/extras/f0dc5336abf293d68280bbd96c39d670.webm?t=1729021181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013490/extras/f0dc5336abf293d68280bbd96c39d670.mp4?t=1729021181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Expansion</h2>Reinvest your earnings to grow your business. Expand the physical size of your range, upgrade facilities, and continuously adapt to meet the evolving needs of the shooting community.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013490/extras/098a4cbe2559ff030108cfb26e50b65e.poster.avif?t=1729021181\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013490/extras/098a4cbe2559ff030108cfb26e50b65e.webm?t=1729021181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013490/extras/098a4cbe2559ff030108cfb26e50b65e.mp4?t=1729021181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>In Shooting Range Simulator, take charge and turn your modest range into a premier shooting venue. Master the art of customer satisfaction and achieve financial success!",
